icit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:11:"description";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:553:"<p>I&#8217;ve been hard at work on the next update to Connections. This update continues my focus on CSV exporting. The new tool adds support to batch export the categories as a CSV file quickly and efficiently. My test database has nearly 2,000 categories and it exports all of them in only a couple seconds. A ...</p>\n<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="http://connections-pro.com/2015/11/27/category-csv-import-and-export/">Category CSV Import and Export</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="http://connections-pro.com">Connections</a>.</p>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:11:"Steven Zahm";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1895:"<p><img class="alignright size-medium wp-image-356424" src="http://connections-pro.com/wp-content/uploads/csv-export-categories-300x182.png" alt="CSV Import/Export Categories" width="300" height="182" srcset="http://connections-pro.com/wp-content/uploads/csv-export-categories-300x182.png 300w, http://connections-pro.com/wp-content/uploads/csv-export-categories-600x365.png 600w, http://connections-pro.com/wp-content/uploads/csv-export-categories.png 602w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" />I&#8217;ve been hard at work on the next update to Connections. This update continues my focus on CSV exporting. The new tool adds support to batch export the categories as a CSV file quickly and efficiently. My test database has nearly 2,000 categories and it exports all of them in only a couple seconds. A great feature of this export is that it will sort the categories alphabetically and then build a hierarchy showing the category parents if you have <strong>nested categories</strong>. So, why is that good news and why would you want that? Well, as an added bonus, this update will also feature <em><strong>bulk importing nested categories</strong></em>, which is a very highly requested feature. This is being added to and included in the <em>free</em> core plugin which means everyone will be able to very easily and quickly import thousands of categories. I&#8217;ll also be including a few sample CSV files for US states, cities and zip codes as free downloads so you&#8217;ll be able to immediately take advantage of this new feature.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="http://connections-pro.com/2015/11/27/category-csv-import-and-export/">Category CSV Import and Export</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="http://connections-pro.com">Connections</a>.</p>\n<img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/connections-pro/news/~4/EYY5eEFO5wI" height="1" width="1" alt=""/>";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:74:"http://connections-pro.com/2015/11/27/category-csv-import-and-export/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"1";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:42:"http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0";a:1:{s:8:"origLink";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:69:"http://connections-pro.com/2015/11/27/category-csv-import-and-export/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}}}s:44:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/syndication/";a:2:{s:12:"updatePeriod";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:6:"hourly";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:15:"updateFrequency";